AN ACTIVE WEATHER PATTERN WILL CONTINUE ACROSS THE STATE INTO FRIDAY MORNING AS A DEEP LOW PRESSURE SYSTEM PASSES TO THE NORTH. THREAT: SIGMET NOVEMBER SERIES FOR EMBD TS TOPS FL450 OVER ISLANDS.
